queries.sql: SELECT *, SUM(`bid_qty_available`) as total_qty, SUM(`bid_qty_available`*`bid_price`) as total_price FROM dbt_biding WHERE (`status`=2 OR `status` = 3) AND `market_symbol`='ETH_BTC' AND `bid_type`='BUY' GROUP BY `dbt_biding`.`bid_price`,`market_symbol`, `bid_type`, `bid_price` ORDER BY `dbt_biding`.`bid_price` asc LIMIT 10
